body_html:
Mac binary for Python3.6 should be uploaded as well.

We still need to do more testing for windows. For anybody feeling adventurous and using python3.6 on windows, could you try pip install -i https://testpypi.python.org/pypi tensorflow and let us know if you see any issue?

body:
Mac binary for Python3.6 should be uploaded as well. 

We still need to do more testing for windows. For anybody feeling adventurous and using python3.6 on windows, could you try `pip install -i https://testpypi.python.org/pypi tensorflow` and let us know if you see any issue?
